Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Catholic Church and Child Sex Abuse
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sxcbz
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 26 Apr 2002
Alistair Cooke considers the scandals of child sex abuse by clergy in the Roman Catholic church and the role of bishops and cardinals in enabling abusers.